Title: National Teachers Day in Afghanistan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs0r
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Afghan teachers being threatened by the Taliban and Al-Qaeda. Also, being a member of AKEL, the communist party in Cyprus. How a piano ended up on the peak of Ben Nevis mountain in Scotland. A discussion on the use of netted or caged beds in mental health institutions. Globalisation and the possible end of siestas in Spain. Afghan women discuss the necessity of university education. Show less